ef=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/fragrance\"\u003efragrance\u003c/a\u003e business, Shapiro is also a longtime \u003cem\u003eNew York Times\u003c/em\u003e beauty columnist as well as the author of \u0026#34;\u003ca href=\"https://bookshop.org/a/81011/9781419726668\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSkin Deep: Women on Skin Care, Makeup, and Looking Their Best\u003c/a\u003e,\u0026#34; a compilation of her best-read columns.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eShe founded Ellis Brooklyn in 2015, and has since grown it to include body care as well as \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/luxury\"\u003eluxury\u003c/a\u003e, \u0026#34;clean\u0026#34; fragrances, partnering with retailers including \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/sephora\"\u003eSephora\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/ulta\"\u003eUlta\u003c/a\u003e and Revolve. In 2023, the company closed a seed round of \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/funding\"\u003efunding\u003c/a\u003e, led by Stage 1 Financials\u0026#39; Stage 1 Fund, which includes Nyx founder Toni Ko.Â \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe\u0026#39;ll discuss all of this and more in our \u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/FM7V\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003elive show\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis conversation will be publicly accessible (no paywall!) on \u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/FM7V\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eThe Fashionista Network\u003c/a\u003e, powered by interactive media platform Fireside, and you\u0026#39